High Quality Video Encoding at Scale

Netflix Technology Blog Blocked Unblock Follow Following Dec 9, 2015

At Netflix we receive high quality sources for our movies and TV shows and encode them to the best video streams possible for a given member’s viewing device and bandwidth capabilities. With the continued growth of our service it has been essential to build a video encoding pipeline that is highly robust, efficient and scalable. Our production system is designed to easily scale
